{"tid":907902,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"IU 演唱會根本粉絲圓夢現場！TWICE 受邀擔任嘉賓，娜璉成功追星","createTime":"2018-11-19T07:48:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T08:21:06.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"70819ac86f7380a9e5d4548917da5021137051a4","tid":907902,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:48:38.000Z","msg":"IU 出道10週年紀念巡迴演唱會《dlwlrma》首爾場11月17、18日連兩日在首爾奧林匹克公園的體操競技場舉辦。而演唱會嘉賓繼釜山場尹鍾信、光州場請夏與首爾第一場god 後，IU 也邀請了喜歡的後輩 TWICE 出席，演唱會簡直是追星圓夢現場！<br />\n<br />\n受邀擔任嘉賓的 TWICE 為大家帶來《TT》與新歌《YES or YES》舞台，台下粉絲熱情地給予應援，就連 IU 都說：「這是 TWICE 的演唱會吧？我聽到粉絲們都一起唱著『太過分~ 太過分~ 』(《TT》歌詞)。就連我的舞者都在後面看著，剛才明明他們的是休息時間！」<br />\n<br />\n▼ TWICE《TT》<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>LIVE</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fLdNT07zQtA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DfLdNT07zQtA&d=ZlhM6C4175W9et9oSJWY30bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=75b6b96e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=fLdNT07zQtA</a><br />\n▼ TWICE《YES or YES》<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">LIVE</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uVbM2pkox-E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DuVbM2pkox-E&d=ZlhM6C4175W9et9oSJWY30bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=9e8170ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uVbM2pkox-E</a><br />\n<br />\n一直以來都是IU 粉絲，透過擔任嘉賓成功追星的娜璉也說：「比起任何舞台都還令人緊張，我們真的很喜歡 IU 前輩，我們都是 TW-aena (TWICE + IU 粉絲名 Uaena)。」<br />\n<br />\n娜璉E條心機女 最中意痴紅人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前子瑜未紅就唔理人 紅左就痴實晒一樣"},{"pid":"3a3d847e4b9ff6f17750442dc3b7342dd0e0f680","tid":907902,"uid":213300,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T07:50:30.000Z","msg":"娜璉真係心機婊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8143eae168cafef7ce6d238ed53c9eb81fba2a4","tid":907902,"uid":52073,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T08:21:06.000Z","msg":"iu沾娜璉光 沾twice光"}]}